  "title": "DRAFTER",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>Prepare and draft steel structure drawings</strong> (shop drawings, as-built drawings) using AutoCAD or similar software.</li>\n  <li><strong>Calculate steel material quantities</strong> based on drawings and project requirements.</li>\n  <li><strong>Prepare and place material orders</strong>, including hollow sections, I-beams, plates, angle bars, and BRC mesh.</li>\n  <li><strong>Coordinate with Main Contractor / Consultants</strong> to resolve technical issues and finalise drawings before execution.</li>\n  <li><strong>Explain drawings to supervisors and workers</strong>, providing technical guidance to ensure correct installation on site.</li>\n  <li><strong>Assist with site coordination</strong> and ensure works are carried out safely and according to specifications.</li>\n  <li><strong>Chinese-speaking candidates will be given priority</strong>, as the role requires daily communication with Chinese-speaking workers.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/Degree in Civil Engineering, Structural Engineering, or related field (fresh graduates welcomed).</li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>AutoCAD</strong> and able to read structural drawings.</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of steel structure components is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and handle multiple tasks.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and teamwork skills.</li>\n</ul>",
